reviewText: The format would not play in America. Why sell it to me?? And what's worse is she is my favorite and I can't watch the show.

This is an absolute must-have from any fan of Peaches. It is extremely fun, full of great songs and props galore! It also includes Peaches early videos from the Teaches of Peaches. This disc came from Germany and is a "region 2' disc (I believe), but it plays perfectly in my American DVD player.
